  "detailed_description": "MY GARAGE is a car simulation game with main focus being simulating real car repair, maintenance and physical behavior. <br />\r\n<br />\r\nCARS<br />\r\n - Damage system so you can fix and replace any of body panels<br />\r\n - Painting system<br />\r\n - Suspension where every part has a usage, wear which affects the handling<br />\r\n - Engine with realistic behavior and components ( down to oil condition affecting wear)<br />\r\n<br />\r\nEnvironment<br />\r\n - Your own garage that you will have to buy parts and tools for <br />\r\n - Tools  - for everything  there is  a special tool - there is even a tire pump lying about somewhere ( you will have to buy a new one if you lose this one)<br />\r\n - Shops -  that sell supplies, car parts, paint and your angle grinder will need new discs, etc.<br />\r\n - Junkyards - where to find car parts or even a whole car if you think it is worth saving<br />\r\n - Barn finds <br />\r\n - Delivery jobs<br />\r\n - More features coming",
  "about_the_game": "MY GARAGE is a car simulation game with main focus being simulating real car repair, maintenance and physical behavior. <br />\r\n<br />\r\nCARS<br />\r\n - Damage system so you can fix and replace any of body panels<br />\r\n - Painting system<br />\r\n - Suspension where every part has a usage, wear which affects the handling<br />\r\n - Engine with realistic behavior and components ( down to oil condition affecting wear)<br />\r\n<br />\r\nEnvironment<br />\r\n - Your own garage that you will have to buy parts and tools for <br />\r\n - Tools  - for everything  there is  a special tool - there is even a tire pump lying about somewhere ( you will have to buy a new one if you lose this one)<br />\r\n - Shops -  that sell supplies, car parts, paint and your angle grinder will need new discs, etc.<br />\r\n - Junkyards - where to find car parts or even a whole car if you think it is worth saving<br />\r\n - Barn finds <br />\r\n - Delivery jobs<br />\r\n - More features coming",
  "supported_languages": "English<strong>*</strong>, Portuguese - Portugal, Portuguese - Brazil, German, Hungarian, Russian, French, Spanish - Spain, Czech, Polish, Swedish<br><strong>*</strong>languages with full audio support",
